  "Description": {
    "English": "Upgrades the metallic shielding of the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Exosuit's gloves</span>.<br><br>An advanced blend of reinforced metal and catalytic shielding allows the user to safely handle <span class=\"name name-catalyst\">hazardous substances</span>, as well as perform the necessary feats of strength required to harvest certain <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">farmable flora</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "升级<span class=\"name name-technology\">套装手套</span>的金属防护。<br><br>通过这种强化金属和催化防护的先进组合，使用者可以安全地处理<span class=\"name name-catalyst\">有害物质</span>，并能得到收获部分<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">可耕种植物</span>所需的力量。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "升級<span class=\"name name-technology\">強化套裝手套</span>的金屬防護層。<br><br>強化金屬與催化防護層兩者的改良混合產品，能讓使用者安全處理<span class=\"name name-catalyst\">危險物質</span>，也能施展出採集特定<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">可栽種植物</span>時所需的必要力量。"
  },
